  <num>31-3175.05</num>
  <heading>Medicaid coverage for medication-assisted treatment.</heading>
  <text>Medicaid shall provide coverage for medication-assisted treatment prescribed for the treatment of substance use disorders; provided, that medication assisted treatment covered in accordance with this section shall not be subject to:</text>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Utilization control, other than those processes specified by the American Society of Addiction Medicine;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Prior authorization;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text>Step therapy; or</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(4)</num>
      <text>Lifetime restriction limits.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
